PLACEHOLDER: overlap.mp3
Description: Subtle audio cue for overlapping speech moments in conversations
Suggested content: Soft background hum or gentle crossfade sound (0.3-0.8 seconds)
Usage: Triggered by [SFX: overlap] cues when speakers talk simultaneously
Recommended volume: -22dB to -18dB normalized (softer than interruptions)
Format: MP3, 128kbps minimum
